::DevilDuer::

DevilDuer nods, his mind working over Diamond's story.

"Dead bot's ain't that useful," he finally says, "Better if ya can 
corrupt them and get them to serve ya. The Predacon council would be 
alot better off if they gained controll of the Maixmal council, not 
killed them."
